features: Pre-rolled Convenience - As the perfect disposable utensils, you don't even have to worry about buying napkins. Our silver silverware set, paired with these pre-rolled napkins, makes your event a breeze.
Safe Disposable Silverware Set - This silver plastic cutlery is 100% food-grade, made from BPA-free and heavy-duty plastic, ensuring minimal cracks and breakage during transportation and use.

Elegant Silverware - These wrapped plastic cutlery sets go above and beyond any plain white or transparent plastic cutlery sets. With crisp white napkins and exquisite silverware, your parties are elevated with elegance and luxury.

Perfect for Any Occasion - Whether it's birthdays, kids' parties, banquets, weddings, or various holidays like Valentine's Day, St. Patrick's Day, Easter, graduation season, Mother's Day, Father's Day, Halloween, Thanksgiving, Christmas, you name it, our rolled silverware disposable is ready to impress.

WHAT'S YOU GET - A convenient 50-pack that includes 50 forks, 50 spoons and 50 knives. Our disposable pre rolled silverware ensure a hassle-free post-party experience, freeing you to savor moments with family and friends instead of worrying about cleanup.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for Thanksgiving/Holidays
reviews.reviewText: I ordered these in silver for a work event last month. They looked beautiful so when I decided to host Friendsgiving this weekend, these were my immediate go to. The table looked great and so did the crackers that I also placed on the table. See other review for the party crackers. :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Vibrant color. Nice packaging. Sturdy silverware. Purchased this product for Thanksgiving and tested one set out. I’m very excited to have the silverware presented like this so myself or my guests will not have to keep jumping up to get the silverware they forgot. And the napkins are very sturdy as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars great item for a rush event
reviews.reviewText: I had a quick event and these worked out great! I only had to leave these out so guests could pick up as they go through the buffet line.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars They're Stong Enough
reviews.reviewText: I served seafood stew (crab legs, other shellfish) and ribs. The silverware performed well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Received the package today and opened right away to find the first bundle with some of the knives snapped off. Disappointed as I don’t have enough time before my event to return and exchange so will make do, but would be great to discuss a partial refund even at this point. Otherwise, these look very nice and are super convenient. Just worried that they snapped in transit and how sturdy will they be when used.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good value set!
reviews.reviewText: Very elegant looking disposable utensil set. Great for holiday parties or events with semi-formal settings. Sturdy and durable. There were some few black dots on the utensils but not noticeable. The knapkins are thick and good quality. Good value set.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Great Way to Set Tables Without Breaking the Bank
reviews.reviewText: As father of the bride, I had to pay the lion's share of my daughter's wedding. These came in very handy and helpful, saving time and money. The utensils are metallic, so they have the look of silverware and are very strong. The colors of the utensils and napkins matched they rest of the wedding tables and did not in any way cheapen the affair. These are a great way to set tables without breaking the bank.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Silverware was great, the napkins were a bit thin.
reviews.reviewText: The napkins were very thin, so we had to supply additional napkins for guests to our wedding. The plastic silverware however was sturdy. We loved the colors, as they reflected 1 of our wedding colors.
